FBIS3-27281 "drchi035_d_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 Northeast Asia Li Lanqing Meets Japanese Business Delegation OW1902083394 Beijing XINHUA in English 0738 GMT 19 Feb 94 OW1902083394 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, February 19 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Li Lanqing met here this afternoon with Tomio Futami, president of the Japanese Hino Motors, Ltd., and his party. They exchanged views on issues of common interest. The Japanese visitors are here as guests of the Machine-Building Ministry of China.
